.TH "drm_lspcon_set_mode" 9 "drm_lspcon_set_mode" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
drm_lspcon_set_mode \- Change LSPCON's mode of operation by writing offset (0x80, 0x40)
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" drm_lspcon_set_mode
.BI "(struct i2c_adapter *adapter "  ","
.BI "enum drm_lspcon_mode mode "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "adapter" 12
I2C-over-aux adapter
.IP "mode" 12
required mode of operation
.SH "RETURN"
0 on success, -error on failure/timeout
